detail.name: Aerodrome Finance
detail.public_notice: Aerodrome has announced that they are investigating a potential DNS hijacking affecting their primary domain. Users are strongly advised not to access or interact with any Aerodrome-related domains until the team confirms that the issue has been resolved. For more information, please refer to the official announcement here.

description.en: Aerodrome Finance is a next-generation AMM designed to serve as Base's central liquidity hub, combining a powerful liquidity incentive engine, vote-lock governance model, and friendly user experience. Aerodrome inherits the latest features from Velodrome V2.
